{"type": "article", "id": 60072, "title": "MAC 和王者荣耀联名推出口红，百事在金球奖颁奖礼发了一支科幻广告 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-08T06:23:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12074, "name": "口红"}, {"id": 4891, "name": "金球奖"}, {"id": 4877, "name": "百事"}, {"id": 45030, "name": "MAC"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/2019010813234478YsMr9DaNUGQR4f.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"lmUy\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MxNGJMBaUTk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>云闪付联合 9 位明星，组成“红包大使天团”。</b></a>用户下载和使用云闪付都有机会获得红包。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132438gdFi7hU1YuSCneEw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.531754\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132438ey8aL4XbNozBJdvk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.532701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132439uBGOzy8xvYsWElRU.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.533207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132555xy7gZXvrCGd9YbIK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.533207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132440PZoWw6O9nNjfybHe.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.531754\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132440dMlfcO2P49KJZyjb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.533207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132439tDEX7GkyZplWmi0F.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.531754\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901081324412TvXpCNfYeal4tFL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.531754\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901081324414JM57ltPRL6EXDIk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.533207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"HoOj\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/f8T6y54Ap0pXYXRSA7fg2g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>M.A.C和王者荣耀联名推出 5 款限定英雄唇膏，</b></a>每种色号分别对应游戏中的一位女英雄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901081327383nw5EVg8M1afY7Zb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019010813273863yEO271shPnQkg5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132739be8ONzwTxnV2ZBuk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108132739tpv2ZIf9jUFdYQsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"4A7L\">肯德基联合上海美术电影制片厂，<b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MzYxMjI0NQ==&amp;mid=2659129828&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=3927977c2772335148dc82d40f0184bd&amp;chksm=bd1fd15e8a685848cedd7043213c3af53d771c4c92f9258367f440c384c43a18f592cc46d81e&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0108RWgY90OMw7vSO3UjxpqZ&amp;key=f138c042e63999ffe97535d1ed45daafad89866e16fa0b290ba1b1af95db46855948865f6e4d3759dd6ba4987ecf1c7996ccb73e6cd8ee3398253d2ef6b8b7a436ef70b23482c0441ddcd20b0fa16bdc&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=DmzE5C%2FFYrmSB5a%2BmZlUrN9dB9uOpl8PwBCkqMEjonjP73gApt3MajO9kEUGDjG3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">推出“国漫守护人”投票活动</a>，</b>让消费者选择想在大银幕上看到的经典动画片。同时发布了纪录片，讲述国漫复刻背后的故事。</p><p line=\"4A7L\" class=\"\">此外，肯德基最近还会发售“天书奇谭限量礼盒”，推出“新春英雄套餐”包含国漫小英雄玩具。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h0823wil8fw\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"PUxZ\" class=\"\">百事在今年金球奖颁奖礼上发布了一支<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w_t3Ax-c19g\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <b>“The Encounter（偶遇者）”</b></a>的科幻广告。主角由演员 William H. Macy 饰演，他破译了外星来客投射的圆形符号，正好是百事的 Logo。创意广告代理 Goodby Silverstein &amp; Partners。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e0824or25y9\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"InQR\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/thomas-cook-the-man-always-wakes-different-bed-albion/1522049\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Thomas Cook 酒店的新广告展现了主角每天从不同地方醒来，</b></a>悬崖，监狱等各种奇葩的环境，每晚都像一场噩梦，建议消费者选择它们从而得到一晚好眠。创意代理商是 Albion。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p0824zh2k52\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"S9hn\"><b>日本镰仓衬衫正式进入中国市场，</b>除了官网之外，目前只在天猫旗舰店售卖。这可能和国内商场昂贵的租金有关，2018 年 12 月时候曾在上海静安寺地铁 10 号出口的聚集地漫选开设快闪店，不过将于 1 月 31 日闭店，店内只能体验，无法直接购买商品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901081330070TMXNYKxi1QInEZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108133007t6VvSfANOz7kHu9x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108133007ZqWCceDj9NGaJHUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"6B4u\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4NjU2NDYyNA==&amp;mid=2247484438&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=49afcd5614f9b6bda2069d23ee0de998&amp;chksm=fdf81169ca8f987f8bb723d6de738377416662a6614d30e0fdbb3e940b7158d6fd744f5a66f7&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1&amp;key=6cfda8fba7586e9a264aeac91b670730bb321d0087bbd1bd15d989fc79ac33cfcec8eb6eec58f5b5ba39f339acf2117ee4f6035bbe768dab2419a8c4bf2565739f91619546de1481339b8d46e98e2176&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=DmzE5C%2FFYrmSB5a%2BmZlUrN9dB9uOpl8PwBCkqMEjonjP73gApt3MajO9kEUGDjG3  \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>抖音将于 1 月 10 日开设线上快闪店，首个合作品牌是刚刚独立的红米手机。</b></a>其实就是抖音原来商品橱窗功能新加了竖屏页面，缩短了购买决策路径。</p><p line=\"4v8T\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/agency-news/choice-hotels-taps-mckinney-creative-agency-record/316148/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>MCKINNEY 成为精品国际酒店的创意代理商，</b></a>之前代理商是麦肯广告。MCKINNEY 将会运营包括广告、数字化、社交等在内的账户，以及酒店旗下各个品牌的策略和创意开发。</p><p line=\"kAI4\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/special-report-super-bowl/pepsico-plug-flagship-cola-doritos-bubly-water-super-bowl/316150/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百事透露了今年的超级碗计划。</b></a>经典产品百事可乐、Doritos 玉米片和诞生不久的气泡水 Bubly 会出现在这场广告游戏中，每个都将会用 30 秒时间展现。创意代理商是 Goodby 和 Silverstein &amp; Partners。</p><p line=\"9D8f\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/agency-news/tbwa-tool-connect-agencies-diverse-vendors/316156/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>TBWA 创建了一个新网站 “OneSandbox”，</b></a>这是个搜索平台，旨在使代理商和创意供应商之间建立联系。供应商主要专注于多元文化和女性议题。</p><p line=\"9D8f\" class=\"\">题图来自：“The Encounter” 视频截图</p>"}